"@JeffHoogland @firefox @googlechrome Friendly advice: do not set a passphrase on Chrome. By default, e2e is disabled in Chrome. Setting a passphrase enables it and you might end up in the same situation as you did with Firefox sync. https://t.co/ODBYI893P7 #fxhelp"

"@neauoire @RoLLodeQc @firefox @BeakerBrowser @brave Probably <link rel="license" href="..."> in your index.html
